data.description: Prepare to be impressed by this BEAUTIFUL NEW 2-story home in the Kingston Park Community! The elegant Gardner Plan boasts a flex space and a guest suite with a walk-in closet on the main floor. The kitchen features gorgeous cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless-steel appliances (includes range, microwave, and dishwasher). All other bedrooms are on the 2nd floor. The oversized primary suite has a private bath with dual vanity sinks and a walk-in closet. This desirable plan also comes complete with a 2-car garage.
